[inn_u_sit]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Come, sit down, Overling, and have some Mhulliq'n'Shrooms with us. The cantina here serves the best of traditional Underling cuisine. There's always some kind of meat - be it Mhulliq, Skrubb, or Angler - and two or three side dishes made from various Shrooms.";
	}
}
[inn_v_sit]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "We've come from far, far away, to do trade in Sadowland. We took the route through Underland as we knew the Underlings are nice people and make good Champignon beer. But on the way down we were attacked by these crazy Crystal Warriors - I could have never imagined such a thing! Now we've lost our wares and have been stuck down here for a week.";
	}
}

[back1]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "How's the situation in the Overlands, all good up there? Also not? Well, well.
I've visited the surface once. Frankly I can't understand how you people can live up there. Nothing above your head, just this endless void, with this weird fireball a'burning in it? And so much weather! I liked the clouds, though. They're kinda funny.";
	}
}
[back2]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Greetings, Overling, pleased to meet ya. How's it going up there?
I've been to the Overlands a few times, yes. Everyone should go and see the Sky at least once. To us Underlings, it is an abominable thing, but I guess you people are used to it. Same goes for the color of your plants - the forests, the meadows, it's all this hideous green! But kinda fascinating, I mean.";
	}
}
